Preconditions:
- The input string `colors` is not null.
- The input array `neededTime` is not null.
- The length of `colors` is equal to the length of `neededTime`.
- The length of `colors` is greater than 1.

Postconditions:
- The output is an integer representing the minimum time Bob needs to make the rope colorful.
- The output is non-negative.
- The output is the minimum time among all possible ways to remove balloons to make the rope colorful.